@model HakaTech.Portal.Models.Domain.QuoteRequest
@using HakaTech.Portal.Models.Domain
@using HakaTech.Portal.Models.ViewModels
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = $"Tarjouspyyntö #{Model.Id}";
    var updateModel = ViewBag.UpdateModel as QuoteRequestUpdateViewModel;
}

<div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-3">
    <a asp-action="Requests" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm">
        <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i>
    </a>
    <h2 class="mb-0"><i class="bi bi-envelope-open me-2"></i>Tarjouspyyntö #@Model.Id</h2>
</div>

@if (TempData["SuccessMessage"] is string sMsg)
{
    <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
        <i class="bi bi-check-circle me-1"></i>@sMsg
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
    </div>
}

<div class="row g-4">

    @* Vasemmalle: tiedot *@
    <div class="col-md-7">
        <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 mb-3">
            <div class="card-body">
                <dl class="row mb-0">
                    <dt class="col-sm-4 text-muted small">Palvelu</dt>
                    <dd class="col-sm-8 fw-semibold">@(Model.Service?.Name ?? "—")</dd>

                    <dt class="col-sm-4 text-muted small">Asiakas</dt>
                    <dd class="col-sm-8">@(Model.Customer?.CompanyName ?? "—")</dd>

                    <dt class="col-sm-4 text-muted small">Pyytäjä</dt>
                    <dd class="col-sm-8">
                        @(Model.CreatedByUser?.FullName.Length > 0
                            ? Model.CreatedByUser.FullName
                            : Model.CreatedByUser?.Email ?? "—")
                    </dd>

                    <dt class="col-sm-4 text-muted small">Lähetetty</dt>
                    <dd class="col-sm-8">@Model.CreatedAt.ToString("dd.MM.yyyy HH:mm")</dd>

                    <dt class="col-sm-4 text-muted small">Päivitetty</dt>
                    <dd class="col-sm-8">@Model.UpdatedAt.ToString("dd.MM.yyyy HH:mm")</dd>

                    <dt class="col-sm-4 text-muted small">Tila</dt>
                    <dd class="col-sm-8">
                        <span class="badge @BadgeClass(Model.Status)">@StatusLabel(Model.Status)</span>
                    </dd>
                </dl>
            </div>
        </div>

        @if (!string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(Model.Message))
        {
            <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
                <div class="card-header small fw-semibold">
                    <i class="bi bi-chat-left-text me-1"></i>Asiakkaan viesti
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">@Model.Message</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        }
    </div>

    @* Oikealle: admin-toiminnot *@
    <div class="col-md-5">
        <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
            <div class="card-header small fw-semibold">
                <i class="bi bi-sliders me-1"></i>Päivitä tila
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <form asp-action="UpdateRequest" method="post">
                    @Html.AntiForgeryToken()
                    <input type="hidden" name="Id" value="@Model.Id" />

                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label fw-semibold">Tila</label>
                        <select name="Status" class="form-select">
                            @foreach (QuoteRequestStatus s in Enum.GetValues<QuoteRequestStatus>())
                            {
                                if (Model.Status == s)
                                {
                                    <option value="@s" selected>@StatusLabel(s)</option>
                                }
                                else
                                {
                                    <option value="@s">@StatusLabel(s)</option>
                                }
                            }
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label fw-semibold">Muistiinpanot <span class="text-muted">(sisäiset)</span></label>
                        <textarea name="AdminNotes" class="form-control" rows="5"
                                  placeholder="Omat muistiinpanot tarjouksesta…">@Model.AdminNotes</textarea>
                    </div>

                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100">
                        <i class="bi bi-check-lg me-1"></i>Tallenna
                    </button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@functions {
    static string StatusLabel(QuoteRequestStatus s) => s switch
    {
        QuoteRequestStatus.Pending    => "Odottaa",
        QuoteRequestStatus.InProgress => "Käsittelyssä",
        QuoteRequestStatus.Sent       => "Lähetetty",
        QuoteRequestStatus.Accepted   => "Hyväksytty",
        QuoteRequestStatus.Declined   => "Hylätty",
        _                             => s.ToString()
    };

    static string BadgeClass(QuoteRequestStatus s) => s switch
    {
        QuoteRequestStatus.Pending    => "bg-warning text-dark",
        QuoteRequestStatus.InProgress => "bg-primary",
        QuoteRequestStatus.Sent       => "bg-info text-dark",
        QuoteRequestStatus.Accepted   => "bg-success",
        QuoteRequestStatus.Declined   => "bg-secondary",
        _                             => "bg-secondary"
    };
}
